  <brief_title>The Effect of Femoral Nerve Block on Postoperative Opioid Use After Anterior Cruciate Ligament (ACL) Reconstruction</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Femoral Nerve Block on Opioid Requirements Following Anterior Cruciate Ligament Reconstruction: A Double Blind, Prospective Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
