  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study evaluates the effect of a femoral nerve block on opioid requirements following
      anterior cruciate ligament (ACL) reconstruction. This is a double blind, prospective
      randomized controlled trial.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
